text:
[Verse]
Paper planes fly high tonight
In the breeze they catch the light
From my window watch them soar
Never seen a sight so pure

[Verse 2]
Fold and toss they glide so free
Simple dreams in harmony
In the sky they leave a trail
Little notes without a fail

[Chorus]
Fly fly don't look back
In the wind leave a track
Fly high reach the stars
Little planes of ours

[Verse 3]
Every plane a whispered wish
Gliding on a night like this
From my heart to yours it goes
Love that only paper shows

[Chorus]
Fly fly don't look back
In the wind leave a track
Fly high reach the stars
Little planes of ours

[Bridge]
Catching moments in the air
Silent messages we share
In the night we are a pair
Paper wings without a care
title: Paper Airplanes
